{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"95ae1dfb0a","title":"关于支左问题的指示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"ed180347a6","index":0,"year":1967,"month":11,"day":5,"articleId":"95ae1dfb0a","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"指示","id":"2d13338754","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"林彪","id":"44b4a39710","type":"人物"},{"name":"郑维山","id":"4dc98f7261","type":"人物"},{"name":"军队和军事","id":"6f7a683373","type":"主题"},{"name":"关键人物文稿","id":"c20d333791","type":"文稿大类"},{"name":"林彪","id":"cce608ea44","type":"主题"},{"name":"个人崇拜","id":"eb3ed1b86b","type":"主题"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第一版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"f326d8be5e","name":"林彪"}]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"a481936b18","type":"title","text":"关于支左问题的指示","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"95ae1dfb0a","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"4821b8a06d","type":"paragraph","text":"要学老三篇，破“私”立公。共产主义就是讲的一个公字，反对一个“私”字。要破“私”立公，不然就在那里扯皮。要解决问题，就要从灵魂深处爆发革命。有错误不改，就是不好，干部、战士，不要以为学了毛主席著作就行了，学了不用那是空话。","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"95ae1dfb0a","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"65d8b41d77","type":"paragraph","text":"千头万绪就是要破“私”。破“私”，要打进攻战，光打防御战不是马列主义。拥护我们伟大领袖毛主席的人是革命的，公和“私”的标准就是拥护还是反对我们的伟大领袖毛主席。","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"95ae1dfb0a","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"83d7c2d864","type":"paragraph","text":"（郑维山、陈先瑞汇报工作后林副主席的指示）","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"95ae1dfb0a","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}